<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 09</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.78fr 1.22fr;
      gap: 20mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 82mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .summary-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .summary-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Channel Highlights */
    .highlight-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
    }

    .highlight-card {
      min-height: 38mm;
      padding: 6mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .highlight-card.primary {
      background: var(--green);
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .highlight-label {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .highlight-card.primary .highlight-label {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    .highlight-title {
      margin: 6mm 0 3mm;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 780;
    }

    .highlight-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.4px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .highlight-card.primary .highlight-desc {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }

    /* Main Channel Area */
    .channel-area {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 84mm;
    }

    .channel-panel {
      padding: 7mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .channel-panel.dark {
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.08);
      border-color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
    }

    .panel-label {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
    }

    .panel-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      font-weight: 780;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .panel-desc {
      margin: 5mm 0 0;
      font-size: 9.8px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .logo-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 3.5mm;
      margin-top: 7mm;
    }

    .logo-box {
      height: 15mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.25);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 7px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.7);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .logo-box img {
      max-width: 75%;
      max-height: 60%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .pb-list {
      margin: 7mm 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.18);
    }

    .pb-list li {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 6mm;
      padding: 3mm 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.12);
      font-size: 9px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .pb-list strong {
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 720;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .metric-strip {
      margin-top: 7mm;
      padding-top: 5mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
    }

    .metric-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
    }

    .metric-desc {
      font-size: 8.8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Customers & Channels</div>

          <h1>
            B2B 납품부터<br />
            온라인 소비자 채널까지<br />
            판매 접점을 넓혀갑니다
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 공공기관과 기업 납품을 기반으로 한 B2B 공급 체계와
            쿠팡, 네이버, 카카오 등 온라인 기반 B2C 채널을 함께 운영하고 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-box">
          <div class="summary-title">B2B · B2C</div>
          <div class="summary-text">
            안정적인 납품 경험과 온라인 채널 운영 역량을 바탕으로
            고객 접점을 지속적으로 확장하고 있습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="highlight-grid">
          <div class="highlight-card primary">
            <div class="highlight-label">Supply</div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight-title">B2B</div>
              <p class="highlight-desc">
                공공기관, 기업, 대량 납품 중심의 공급 체계를 운영합니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-label">Retail</div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight-title">B2C</div>
              <p class="highlight-desc">
                온라인 스토어와 선물하기 채널을 통해 소비자 접점을 확대합니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="highlight-card">
            <div class="highlight-label">Partner</div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight-title">PB</div>
              <p class="highlight-desc">
                쿠팡 PB 제품 생산·납품을 통해 제조 파트너십을 확장합니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="channel-area">

          <div class="channel-panel">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-label">Channel Network</div>
              <h3 class="panel-title">
                주요 온라인 판매 채널과<br />
                소비자 접점
              </h3>

              <p class="panel-desc">
                쿠팡, 네이버 스마트스토어, 카카오선물하기 등
                주요 온라인 채널을 통해 브론디 제품의 접근성을 높이고 있습니다.
              </p>

              <div class="logo-grid">
                <div class="logo-box">Coupang</div>
                <div class="logo-box">Naver</div>
                <div class="logo-box">Kakao</div>
                <div class="logo-box">Store</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric-strip">
              <div>
                <div class="metric-title">4.5+</div>
                <div class="metric-desc">
                  온라인 채널 고객 평점 기준
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="metric-title">2,000+</div>
                <div class="metric-desc">
                  고객 댓글 기반 만족도 확인
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="channel-panel dark">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-label">Coupang PB</div>
              <h3 class="panel-title">
                총 7개 쿠팡 PB 제품을<br />
                생산 및 납품하고 있습니다
              </h3>

              <p class="panel-desc">
                두루마리 화장지, 점보롤, 여행용티슈, 포켓티슈 등
                다양한 생활 위생지 품목의 PB 생산 경험을 보유하고 있습니다.
              </p>

              <ul class="pb-list">
                <li>
                  <strong>01</strong>
                  <span>두루마리 화장지</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>02</strong>
                  <span>점보롤</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>03</strong>
                  <span>여행용티슈</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>04</strong>
                  <span>포켓티슈</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>+3</strong>
                  <span>기타 생활 위생지 제품군</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="metric-strip">
              <div>
                <div class="metric-title">No.1</div>
                <div class="metric-desc">
                  쿠팡 점보롤 판매량 기준
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="metric-title">No.1</div>
                <div class="metric-desc">
                  고객 만족도 기준
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">09</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
